{
  "texts": [
    "P8: So I was afraid and felt anxious, yes, because you are using such an environment for the first time.",
    "However, if I wore virtual reality glasses, I could experience this fear more.",
    "When we look at certain places such as spheres in these rooms, rather than the ones created by the school for us, we can walk through different rooms.",
    "In other words, I encountered different things, I saw art galleries where some people displayed their paintings on this platform, and they created spaces where I felt as if I was visiting a gallery.",
    "However, it was a little bit scary when there was no one around me."
  ]
}